OL,3,CScottish government vows to ditch two-
OL,4,Cchild benefit cap
OL,6,FScotland's Finance Secretary Shona
OL,7,FRobison promised to lift 15,000
OL,8,Fchildren out of poverty as she made
OL,9,Fher Budget announcement, ITV News
OL,10,FCorrespondent Peter Smith reports
OL,12,FThe Scottish government will abolish
OL,13,Fthe two-child benefit cap, in a move
OL,14,FFinance Secretary Shona Robison says
OL,15,Fwill lift 15,000 children out of
OL,16,Fpoverty.
