OL,3,CScottish government vows to ditch two-
OL,4,Cchild benefit cap
OL,6,FSetting out her draft Budget at
OL,7,FHolyrood on Wednesday, Robison said
OL,8,Fthere was no doubt "the cap will be
OL,9,Fscrapped", and that SNP ministers
OL,10,Fwould aim to provide funding to
OL,11,Faffected families by 2026.
OL,13,FThe two-child cap prevents parents
OL,14,Ffrom claiming universal credit or
OL,15,Fchild tax credit for a third child, a
OL,16,Fpolicy which was introduced by the
OL,17,Fprevious government in 2017.
