OL,3,CScottish government vows to ditch two-
OL,4,Cchild benefit cap
OL,6,FMinisters north of the border have
OL,7,Fcontinually hit out at the policy for
OL,8,Fyears, which has not been scrapped by
OL,9,Fthe new Labour administration.
OL,11,FCalling on the UK government to
OL,12,Fprovide the necessary data to allow
OL,13,Ffor the change to be made, Robison
OL,14,Fsaid: "My challenge to Labour is to
OL,15,Fwork with us - join us in ending the
OL,16,Fcap in Scotland, give us the
OL,17,Finformation that we need.
