OL,3,CScottish government vows to ditch two-
OL,4,Cchild benefit cap
OL,6,F"But either way, let me be crystal
OL,7,Fclear, this government is to end the
OL,8,Ftwo-child cap and in doing so will
OL,9,Flift over 15,000 Scottish children out
OL,10,Fof poverty."
OL,12,FShe also announced changes to
OL,13,FScotland's income tax band, allowing
OL,14,Fmore of people's earnings to be levied
OL,15,Fat lower rates.
OL,17,FRobison claimed this would mean that
OL,18,Fthe majority of people in Scotland
OL,19,Fwould pay less income tax than if they
OL,20,Flived elsewhere in the UK.
