OL,4,Cchild benefit cap
OL,6,FThe draft Budget also included:
OL,8,FScottish Labour finance spokesperson
OL,9,FMichael Marra said the Budget was an
OL,10,Fopportunity for the SNP to take
OL,11,FScotland in a new direction, after the
OL,12,FUK government provided #3.4bn of
OL,13,Fadditional funding.
OL,15,F"If only they had the imagination to
OL,16,Ftake that new direction," he told
OL,17,FMSPs. "Scotland is going in the wrong
OL,18,Fdirection under the SNP."
